snippet.title: Statistics - Probability using "OR", and ODDS
snippet.description:
What is the chance of this happening OR that happening? Here, the "Preppy Roman" dives into that very question. We cover the definition of "mutually exclusive", then also cover the definition of ODDS and try a few practice scenarios. YAY MATH! (HD)
Please visit yaymath.org
